dct_title_s: Stokes State Forest, New Jersey 1948 maps
dct_description_sm: Maps of Stokes State Forest in Sussex County, N.J. part of multi-page brochure. These sheets are two maps of area. First includes inset guide to Kittle Field. Second map shows Tillman Ravine with inset of the western section of the park. Legends indicate paved roads, unpaved trails, streams and other waterways, camp grounds and park office.
